name: Laws of Karma — #1 The Great Law
description:
Welcome to my "Laws of Karma" series. There'll be 12 laws and this is the first one called The Great Law (also known as The Law of Cause and Effect).

The wisdom said if you share love and kindness, you shall get that in return. That's pretty much explain why the cat who gave up his one and only food to a chick, got twice as many foods he had before.

It's just the way the Universe gives back :)
